{"id": 1991, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X汉莎航空】为了长途飞行更自在，你都做过哪些“努力”？", "description": "没有什么长途飞行是不能用睡一觉战胜的，如果有，那就再睡一觉。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 7790, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171103155059o649wlsEZtiUQLdD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-07T03:00:52Z", "options": [{"id": 246784, "content": "睡觉 一定要睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 629215}, {"id": 246785, "content": "看电影吃零食睡觉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024356}, {"id": 246786, "content": "问空姐要一个小靠枕 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176704}, {"id": 247042, "content": "带上耳塞和眼罩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178650}, {"id": 246787, "content": "努力赚钱挣机票", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122421}, {"id": 255235, "content": "落地才能把我震醒的角色，占个方块……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753433}, {"id": 246788, "content": "我喜欢在起飞后喝酒，差不多把自己喝到疲倦了，自然而然就睡着了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097425}, {"id": 246789, "content": "机舱里超级干燥，敷高保湿面膜", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107204}, {"id": 246790, "content": "顺其自然，选对航空公司很重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136399}, {"id": 246792, "content": "狠心花了2700买了bose降噪耳机 之后每次坐飞机都觉得这2700花的是近些年最划算的一笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735119}, {"id": 246793, "content": "上机就睡觉，睡醒了吃，然后再睡，然后看书！然后看剧然后再睡！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969118}, {"id": 246794, "content": "和用户聚会", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1177723}, {"id": 246795, "content": "睡觉三宝，眼罩 U型枕 毯子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107407}, {"id": 246796, "content": "攒钱买头等舱，攒不够就忍着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 247308, "content": "选最后几排的位子 通常会空 还方便找空乘要喝的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585041}, {"id": 246797, "content": "给我酒", "image": "img/option/option/20171107144119xWCIe3ko5jndH98t.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584690}, {"id": 246798, "content": "买商务舱", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234006}, {"id": 246799, "content": "在机场买好各种食物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001167}, {"id": 246800, "content": "远离隔壁的孩子們????", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733477}, {"id": 246802, "content": "从起飞睡到降落，睡的昏天暗地~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752698}, {"id": 246803, "content": "看杂志，带零食", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1171765}, {"id": 246804, "content": "带kindle", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449790}, {"id": 246805, "content": "眼罩\n耳机\n当下有兴趣想看的剧目\n书本", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153320}, {"id": 246809, "content": "一个颈枕，一条毛毯，一副耳机，一趟舒服的旅程?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107203}, {"id": 246811, "content": "结伴出行，斗会儿地主", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614051}, {"id": 246818, "content": "赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937983}, {"id": 246821, "content": "睁开眼-饮料小车车来了-再睁眼-晚饭小车车来了-再再睁眼-宵夜小车车来了-再再再睁眼-早饭小车车来了.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1177832}, {"id": 249639, "content": "坐IMA航空", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186524}, {"id": 246827, "content": "尽量别和胖子和情侣坐。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155928}, {"id": 246828, "content": "晕车药！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140460}, {"id": 246830, "content": "努力不出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360886}, {"id": 247089, "content": "一个效果优秀的降噪耳机很重要很重要很重要!!!", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178818}, {"id": 246836, "content": "提前两天不睡觉，上飞机一觉睡到大天亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 384636}, {"id": 246840, "content": "给自己定闹钟，每四个小时起来去厕所里做伸展运动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760231}, {"id": 246841, "content": "耳塞，眼罩，漂亮小姐姐用过【划掉】发的毛毯，美美的睡一觉，完美", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084868}, {"id": 247097, "content": "提前两个小时去机场选安全门旁边位置只为能伸直腿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565391}, {"id": 246842, "content": "恐惧—— ，长途恐惧症", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697539}, {"id": 246844, "content": "带本书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173461}, {"id": 246845, "content": "换套睡衣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176545}, {"id": 248893, "content": "长时间飞行的时候真敷了个面膜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766872}, {"id": 246847, "content": "迭代成长", "image": "img/option/option/20171107181121Od2Yvjnsf63oJbDH", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173389}, {"id": 246848, "content": "买了bose qc30", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341831}, {"id": 246849, "content": "一路霸占厕所…算不算…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669037}, {"id": 246850, "content": "提前好久就开始抢座位", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484106}, {"id": 246851, "content": "根据目的地时差调整机上睡眠时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456678}, {"id": 246852, "content": "QC35", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341793}, {"id": 246853, "content": "带上拖鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026074}, {"id": 246854, "content": "海南航空机尾有bar，不断往那跑拿吃的和喝的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144138}, {"id": 246855, "content": "只坐空客飞机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507280}, {"id": 246856, "content": "惊了，好奇心都开始接汉莎的广告了！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273098}]}